text:

I've been really annoyed lately in getting a good content feed. Its a mix of a traditional RSS app but you could also important things from Twitter and other websites.

Ask HN: How do you ramp up on a new job?
text:
Hello,

I am about to start a new job working on a huge established code base. The existing team is about 15-20 people and am going to be joining as a staff engineer. I have been thinking about what would my initial days/weeks look like outside of the companies onboarding meetings.

Do you setup 1-1s with everyone on the team? How do you go about figuring out the right areas to contribute? How should I work on building relationships in the initial days?

title: Ask HN: How to transfer all Chrome/Brave custom settings to Edge?
text:
I'm talking about extensions AND extension settings, as well as all custom search engines and custom keyboard shortcuts.

Are these settings saved as files somewhere? If I move them to Edge's folder, would it be able to read them?

I'm on macOS.
